EN-US'>v</span>, что и требовалось. Случай (<span style='font-family:Symbol;
mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol'>&Oslash;</span><span style='mso-fareast-language:
EN-US'>A&nbsp;</span>&amp;&nbsp;<span style='mso-fareast-language:EN-US'>A</span>*)
