style='mso-fareast-language:EN-US'>v</span>, <span style='font-family:Symbol;
mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol'>&Oslash;</span>А* выполнена в структуре &lt;U,&nbsp;F&gt;
при оценке <span style='mso-fareast-language:EN-US'>v</span>. Значит, в
структуре &lt;U,&nbsp;F&gt; при оценке <span style='mso-fareast-language:EN-US'>v</span>
выполнена конъюнкция (А&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;<span style='font-family:Symbol;
mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-language:EN-US'>&Oslash;</span><span
style='mso-fareast-language:EN-US'>A</span>*) и, следовательно, дизъюнкция ((А&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;<span
style='font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-language:
EN-US'>&Oslash;</span><span style='mso-fareast-language:EN-US'>A</span>*)&nbsp;<span
style='font-family:Symbol;mso-ascii-font-family:"Times New Roman";mso-hansi-font-family:
"Times New Roman";mso-char-type:symbol;mso-symbol-font-family:Symbol'><span
style='mso-char-type:symbol;mso-symbol-font-family:Symbol'>&Uacute;</span></span>&nbsp;(<span
style='font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol'>&Oslash;</span><span
style='mso-fareast-language:EN-US'>A&nbsp;</span>&amp;&nbsp;<span
style='mso-fareast-language:EN-US'>A</span>*)), что и требовалось. Вторая
