снимем квантор общности на <span style='font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:
Symbol;mso-fareast-language:EN-US'>e</span>-терм <span style='font-family:Symbol;
mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-language:EN-US'>e</span>хР(х,&nbsp;КГ):
нР(<span style='font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-language:
EN-US'>e</span>хР(х,&nbsp;КГ),&nbsp;КГ)&nbsp;<span style='mso-bidi-font-size:
12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-ascii-font-family:"Times New Roman";mso-hansi-font-family:
"Times New Roman";mso-char-type:symbol;mso-symbol-font-family:Symbol'><span
