Symbol'><span style='mso-char-type:symbol;mso-symbol-font-family:Symbol'>&Icirc;</span></span>&nbsp;T,
б)&nbsp;<span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-ascii-font-family:
"Times New Roman";mso-hansi-font-family:"Times New Roman";mso-char-type:symbol;
